These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
Beverage: hot-chocolate, juice
Pet: chinchilla, horse
1. Pet:chinchilla is somewhere to the right of Beverage:hot-chocolate##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | juice      |
| Pet        | horse         | chinchilla |

 ################################# 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
Movie-Genre: drama, mystery
Sport: volleyball, weightlifting
1. Movie-Genre:mystery is somewhere to the right of Movie-Genre:drama##5
2. Sport:weightlifting is on the left of Sport:volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama         | mystery    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | volleyball |

 ################################# 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
Movie-Genre: comedy, time-travel
Nationality: egyptian, turkish
1. Nationality:turkish is somewhere to the left of Movie-Genre:comedy##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | comedy   |
| Nationality   | turkish     | egyptian |

 ################################# 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
Hobby: chess, video-games
Job: analyst, software-developer
1. Job:software-developer is somewhere to the left of Hobby:chess##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |         1          |    2    |
| Hobby   | video-games        | chess   |
| Job     | software-developer | analyst |

